{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c874cfff30","title":"江青周恩来等接见徒步来京红卫兵时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd7e03107c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"c874cfff30","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李富春","id":"25e2abfb25","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘志坚","id":"5d13a4eb3c","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴德","id":"7f0393737e","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"杨成武","id":"e1397e909a","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"江青，本世纪初国内老左编","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b0aaa51165","type":"title","text":"江青周恩来等接见徒步来京红卫兵时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47a338cd25","type":"paragraph","text":"〖参加接见的还有：康生、李富春、杨成武、张春桥、吴德、刘志坚、彭绍辉等同志。大会开始前，周总理、康生、江青等首长乘车绕场一周，接见和检阅徒步来京的红卫兵代表。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"197be63f2f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志讲话","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73c273af01","type":"appellation","text":"同学们、红卫兵战友们：","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3fdddfefa","type":"paragraph","text":"你们是徒步长征从祖国各地到北京来的，我们欢迎你们，向你们致以无产阶级文化大革命的敬礼！你们是遵照毛主席的教导，发扬艰苦朴素的作风，一路走着来的。你们拜贫下中农为师，拜工人为师，我们向你们学习。道路是曲折的，不平坦的，同志们要有百倍的英勇顽强的精神继续奋斗，祝你们继续完成长征宣传队的任务。我的话完了。","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4d18bdd3a","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来同志讲话","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60c1158172","type":"appellation","text":"同学们、红卫兵战友们：","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c443c1948","type":"paragraph","text":"我现在向你们致以无产阶级文化大革命的战斗的敬礼，让我代表我们伟大的领袖毛主席、林副主席、党中央和国务院问你们好！","index":7,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63cbb89bfa","type":"paragraph","text":"你们从我们祖国各地跋涉千山万水，终于来到我们祖国的首都北京。我们欢迎你们，你们热烈要求见我们伟大的领袖毛主席，我们懂得你们的心情。我现在宣布你们现在回去，到明年春暖季节，我们免费乘车接你们来。","index":8,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8608b949a","type":"paragraph","text":"我很高兴地看到你们学习解放军的精神，有的走两千多里，最远的走五千多里，你们这种精神值得我们学习，值得全国的学生学习。你们自己说得对，这仅仅是万里长征的第一步，你们还要好好学习。要更好地学习解放军的三大纪律、八项注意，做坚强的解放军的后备力量，现在你们快回去了，我们准备免费乘车送你们回去，如果你们愿意徒步回去，那就更好。学习解放军，做战斗队、宣传队、学习队。","index":9,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b28cf8369f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们在长征的途中，吃多了粮食，用多了粮票，我们准备发给你们学校，补助你们。","index":10,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d751f3c302","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们、战友们，你们这种精神要永远保持下去，将来一旦国家有事，你们是最好的解放军的后备队。","index":11,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0128758a0","type":"appellation","text":"同学们、战友们，让我们一起高呼：","index":12,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6bd5cf3a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"长征精神万岁！","index":13,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f5c78ba07","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命万岁！","index":14,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ece827278","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":15,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd86ab29c4","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的毛泽东思想万岁！","index":16,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b2b6c26e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党万岁！","index":17,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4196c34540","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c874cfff30","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":162,"end":161}}}},"__N_SSG":true}